      • add

        public <TResolver extends Resolver<TType>,​TType> ResolverProvider add​(java.lang.Class<TResolver> resolverClass)
        Description copied from interface: ResolverProvider
        Registers the given resolver in this provider.

        The registration will fail and print a log message if the resolver is already registered.

        The resolver must have an parameterless public constructor or else ResolverProvider.add(Class, Supplier) must be used.

        Specified by:

                                                                            java.util.function.Supplier<TResolver> supplier)
        Description copied from interface: ResolverProvider
        Registers the given resolver with the provided method to create it in this provider.

        The registration will fail and print a log message if the resolver is already registered.

        Use the ResolverProvider.add(Class) method if your resolver has a parameterless public constructor.
